HEADWORD: Stanno-
<hw>Stan"no-</hw> <pr>(-n⟦osl⟧-)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>stannum</ets>
tin.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A combining form (also used
adjectively) denoting <sig>relating to tin</sig>, or <sig>connected with
tin</sig>, or indicating <sig>containing tin as an
ingredient</sig>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stannofluoride</ent>⟦br⟧
